#: ../../content/applications/services/helpdesk/overview/sla.rst:3
msgid "Service level agreements (SLA)"
msgstr "Service level agreement (SLA)"

#: ../../content/applications/services/helpdesk/overview/sla.rst:5
msgid ""
"A *service level agreement* (SLA) defines the level of service a customer "
"can expect from a supplier. :abbr:`SLAs (Service Level Agreements)` provide "
"a timeline that tells customers when they can expect results, and keeps the "
"support team on target."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/services/helpdesk/overview/sla.rst:10
msgid ""
"The *SLA Policies* feature is enabled by default on newly created *Helpdesk* "
"teams."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/services/helpdesk/overview/sla.rst:12
msgid ""
"To turn off the feature, or edit the working hours, navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Helpdesk app --> Configuration --> Helpdesk Teams`. Click "
"on a team to open that team's configuration page."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menonaktifkan fitur ini, atau mengedit jam kerja, buka "
":menuselection:`aplikasi Pusat Bantuan --> Konfigurasi --> Tim Pusat "
"Bantuan`. Klik pada tim untuk membuka halaman konfigurasi tim tersebut."

#: ../../content/applications/services/helpdesk/overview/sla.rst:15
msgid ""
"From here, scroll to the :guilabel:`Performance` section. To turn off "
"the :abbr:`SLAs (Service Level Agreements)` feature for the team, clear "
"the :guilabel:`SLA Policies` checkbox."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/services/helpdesk/overview/sla.rst:0
msgid "View of a team page in Helpdesk focusing on the SLA Policies setting."
msgstr ""
"Tampilan halaman tim di Pusat Bantuan yang berfokus pada pengaturan "
"Kebijakan SLA."

#: ../../content/applications/services/helpdesk/overview/sla.rst:23
msgid "Create a new SLA policy"
msgstr "Membuat kebijakan SLA baru"

#: ../../content/applications/services/helpdesk/overview/sla.rst:25
msgid ""
"To create a new policy, go to :menuselection:`Helpdesk app --> Configuration "
"--> SLA Policies`, and click :guilabel:`New`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk membuat kebijakan baru, buka :menuselection:`aplikasi Pusat "
"Bantuan --> Konfigurasi --> Kebijakan SLA`, dan klik :guilabel:`Baru`."

#: ../../content/applications/services/helpdesk/overview/sla.rst:28
msgid ""
"Alternatively, go to :menuselection:`Helpdesk app --> Configuration --> "
"Helpdesk Teams`, and click on a team. Then, click the :guilabel:`SLA "
"Policies` smart button at the top of the team's settings page, and "
"click :guilabel:`New`."
msgstr ""
"Sebagai alternatif, buka :menuselection:`aplikasi Pusat Bantuan --> "
"Konfigurasi --> Tim Pusat Bantuan`, dan klik pada tim. Kemudian, klik tombol "
"pintar :guilabel:`Kebijakan SLA` di bagian atas halaman pengaturan tim, dan "
"klik :guilabel:`Baru`."

#: ../../content/applications/services/helpdesk/overview/sla.rst:32
msgid ""
"On the blank :abbr:`SLA (Service Level Agreement)` policy form, enter "
"a :guilabel:`Title` and a :guilabel:`Description` for the new policy, and "
"proceed to fill out the form using the steps below."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/services/helpdesk/overview/sla.rst:36
msgid "Define the criteria for an SLA policy"
msgstr "Menentukan kriteria untuk kebijakan SLA"

#: ../../content/applications/services/helpdesk/overview/sla.rst:38
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Criteria` section is used to identify which tickets this "
"policy is applied to."
msgstr ""
"Bagian :guilabel:`Kriteria` digunakan untuk mengidentifikasi tiket mana yang "
"diterapkan kebijakan ini."

#: ../../content/applications/services/helpdesk/overview/sla.rst:40
msgid "Fill out the following fields to adjust the selection criteria:"
msgstr "Isi bidang berikut untuk menyesuaikan kriteria seleksi:"

#: ../../content/applications/services/helpdesk/overview/sla.rst:43
msgid ""
"Unless otherwise indicated, multiple selections can be made for each field."
msgstr ""
"Kecuali disebutkan lain, beberapa pilihan dapat dibuat untuk setiap bidang."

#: ../../content/applications/services/helpdesk/overview/sla.rst:45
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Helpdesk Team`: a policy can only be applied to one team. *This "
"field is required.*"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/services/helpdesk/overview/sla.rst:46
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Priority`: the priority level for a ticket is identified by "
"selecting one, two, or three of the :guilabel:`⭐ (star)` icons, "
"representing the priority level on the Kanban card or on the ticket itself. "
"The :abbr:`SLA (Service Level Agreement)` is **only** applied after the "
"priority level has been updated on the ticket to match the :abbr:`SLA "
"(Service Level Agreement)` criteria. If no selection is made in this field, "
"this policy only applies to tickets marked as `Low Priority`, meaning those "
"with zero :guilabel:`⭐ (star)` icons."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/services/helpdesk/overview/sla.rst:52
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Tags`: tags are used to indicate what the ticket is about. "
"Multiple tags can be applied to a single ticket."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/services/helpdesk/overview/sla.rst:54
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Customers`: individual contacts or companies may be selected in "
"this field."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/services/helpdesk/overview/sla.rst:55
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Sales Order Items`: this field is available only if a team has "
"the *Timesheets* app enabled. This allows the ticket to link directly to a "
"specific line on a sales order, which must be indicated on the ticket in "
"the :guilabel:`Sales Order Items` field."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/services/helpdesk/overview/sla.rst:60
msgid ""
"A support team needs to address urgent issues for VIP customers within one "
"business day."
msgstr ""
"Tim dukungan perlu menangani masalah mendesak untuk pelanggan VIP dalam "
"waktu satu hari kerja."

#: ../../content/applications/services/helpdesk/overview/sla.rst:62
msgid ""
"The new policy, titled `8 Hours to close`, is assigned to the `VIP Support` "
"team. It **only** applies to tickets that are assigned three :guilabel:`⭐ "
"(star)` icons, which equates to an `Urgent` priority level."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/services/helpdesk/overview/sla.rst:66
msgid ""
"At the same time, the tickets can be related to multiple issues, so the "
"policy applies to tickets with `Repair`, `Service`, or `Emergency` tags."
msgstr ""
"Pada saat yang sama, tiket dapat terkait dengan beberapa masalah, sehingga "
"kebijakan berlaku untuk tiket dengan tag `Perbaikan`, `Layanan`, atau "
"`Darurat`."

#: ../../content/applications/services/helpdesk/overview/sla.rst:0
msgid ""
"View of a new SLA policy record with all the relevant information entered."
msgstr ""
"Tampilan catatan kebijakan SLA baru dengan semua informasi yang relevan "
"dimasukkan."

#: ../../content/applications/services/helpdesk/overview/sla.rst:74
msgid "Establish a target for an SLA policy"
msgstr "Menetapkan target untuk kebijakan SLA"

#: ../../content/applications/services/helpdesk/overview/sla.rst:76
msgid ""
"A *target* is the stage a ticket needs to reach, and the time allotted to "
"reach that stage, in order to satisfy the :abbr:`SLA (Service Level "
"Agreement)` policy. Any stage assigned to a team may be selected for "
"the :guilabel:`Reach Stage` field."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/services/helpdesk/overview/sla.rst:80
msgid ""
"Time spent in stages selected in the :guilabel:`Excluding Stages` field are "
"**not** included in the calculation of the :abbr:`SLA (Service Level "
"Agreement)` deadline."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/services/helpdesk/overview/sla.rst:84
msgid ""
"An :abbr:`SLA (Service Level Agreement)` titled `8 Hours to Close` tracks "
"the working time before a ticket is completed, and would have `Solved` as "
"the :guilabel:`Reach Stage`. Simultaneously, an :abbr:`SLA (Service Level "
"Agreement)` titled `2 Days to Start` tracks the working time before work on "
"a ticket has begun, and would have `In Progress` as the :guilabel:`Reach "
"Stage`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/services/helpdesk/overview/sla.rst:90
msgid "Meet SLA deadlines"
msgstr "Memenuhi tenggat waktu SLA"

#: ../../content/applications/services/helpdesk/overview/sla.rst:92
msgid ""
"As soon as it is determined that a ticket fits the criteria of an :abbr:`SLA "
"(Service Level Agreement)` policy, a deadline is calculated. The deadline is "
"based on the creation date of the ticket, and the targeted working hours."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/services/helpdesk/overview/sla.rst:97
msgid ""
"The value indicated next to the :guilabel:`Working Hours` field of "
"an :abbr:`SLA (Service Level Agreement)` policy is used to determine the "
"deadline. By default, this is determined by the value set in "
"the :guilabel:`Company Working Hours` field under :menuselection:`Settings "
"app --> Employees --> Work Organization`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/services/helpdesk/overview/sla.rst:102
msgid ""
"The deadline is then added to the ticket, as well as a tag indicating the "
"name of the :abbr:`SLA (Service Level Agreement)` applied."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/services/helpdesk/overview/sla.rst:None
msgid ""
"View of a ticket's form emphasizing an open SLA deadline on a ticket in Odoo "
"Helpdesk."
msgstr ""
"Tampilan formulir tiket yang menekankan tenggat waktu SLA yang terbuka pada "
"tiket di Odoo Pusat Bantuan."

#: ../../content/applications/services/helpdesk/overview/sla.rst:109
msgid ""
"When a ticket satisfies an :abbr:`SLA (Service Level Agreement)` policy, "
"the :abbr:`SLA (Service Level Agreement)` tag turns green, and the deadline "
"disappears from view on the ticket."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/services/helpdesk/overview/sla.rst:None
msgid "View of a ticket's form emphasizing a satisfied SLA in Odoo Helpdesk."
msgstr ""
"Tampilan formulir tiket yang menekankan SLA yang terpenuhi di Pusat Bantuan "
"Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/services/helpdesk/overview/sla.rst:117
msgid ""
"If a ticket fits the criteria for more than one :abbr:`SLA (Service Level "
"Agreement)`, the earliest occurring deadline is displayed on the ticket. "
"After that deadline has passed, the next deadline is displayed."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/services/helpdesk/overview/sla.rst:121
msgid ""
"If the :abbr:`SLA (Service Level Agreement)` deadline passes and the ticket "
"has not moved to the :guilabel:`Reach Stage`, the :abbr:`SLA (Service Level "
"Agreement)` tag turns red. After the :abbr:`SLA (Service Level Agreement)` "
"has failed, the red tag stays on the ticket, even after the ticket is moved "
"to the :guilabel:`Reach Stage`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/services/helpdesk/overview/sla.rst:None
msgid ""
"View of a ticket's form with a failing and passing SLA in Odoo Helpdesk."
msgstr ""
"Tampilan formulir tiket dengan SLA yang gagal dan berhasil di Pusat Bantuan "
"Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/services/helpdesk/overview/sla.rst:133
msgid "Analyze SLA performance"
msgstr "Analisis kinerja SLA"

#: ../../content/applications/services/helpdesk/overview/sla.rst:135
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`SLA Status Analysis` report tracks how quickly an :abbr:`SLA "
"(Service Level Agreement)` is fulfilled, as well as the performance of "
"individual team members. Navigate to the report, and corresponding pivot "
"table, by going to :menuselection:`Helpdesk app --> Reporting --> SLA Status "
"Analysis`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/services/helpdesk/overview/sla.rst:143
msgid ""
"By default, the report displays in a :guilabel:`Pivot` view. Any :abbr:`SLA "
"(Service Level Agreement)` policies in the database with tickets that failed "
"to fulfill a policy, are in progress, or have satisfied a policy are listed. "
"By default, they are grouped by team and ticket count."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/services/helpdesk/overview/sla.rst:151
msgid ""
"The pivot view aggregates data, which can be manipulated by adding measures "
"and filters."
msgstr ""
"Tampilan pivot menggabungkan data, yang dapat dimanipulasi dengan "
"menambahkan ukuran dan filter."

#: ../../content/applications/services/helpdesk/overview/sla.rst:153
msgid ""
"To change the display, or add additional measurements, click "
"the :guilabel:`Measures` button to reveal a drop-down menu of reporting "
"criteria, and choose from the options available."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengubah tampilan atau menambahkan pengukuran tambahan, klik tombol "
":guilabel:`Measures` untuk menampilkan menu drop-down kriteria pelaporan, "
"dan pilih dari opsi yang tersedia."

#: ../../content/applications/services/helpdesk/overview/sla.rst:156
msgid ""
"Whenever a measurement is picked, a :guilabel:`✔️ (checkmark)` icon appears "
"in the drop-down menu to indicate that the measurement is included, and a "
"corresponding new column emerges in the pivot table to show the relevant "
"calculations."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/services/helpdesk/overview/sla.rst:None
msgid "View of the available measures in the SLA status analysis report."
msgstr "Tampilan ukuran yang tersedia dalam laporan analisis status SLA."

#: ../../content/applications/services/helpdesk/overview/sla.rst:164
msgid ""
"To add a group to a row or column, click the :guilabel:`➕ (plus)` icon next "
"to the policy name and then select one of the groups. To remove one, click "
"the :guilabel:`➖ (minus)` icon next to the policy name."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/services/helpdesk/overview/sla.rst:None
msgid ""
"View of the available group by options in the SLA status analysis report."
msgstr ""
"Tampilan opsi pengelompokan yang tersedia dalam laporan analisis status SLA."

#: ../../content/applications/services/helpdesk/overview/sla.rst:175
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`SLA Status Analysis` report can also be viewed as "
"a :guilabel:`Bar Chart`, :guilabel:`Line Chart`, or :guilabel:`Pie Chart`. "
"Toggle between these views by first selecting the :guilabel:`Graph` button "
"at the top-right of the dashboard. Then, select the appropriate chart icon "
"at the top-left of the graph."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/services/helpdesk/overview/sla.rst:182
msgid "Bar Chart"
msgstr "Bagan Bilah"

#: ../../content/applications/services/helpdesk/overview/sla.rst:188
msgid ""
"A bar chart can deal with larger data sets and compare data across several "
"categories."
msgstr ""
"Grafik batang dapat menangani kumpulan data yang lebih besar dan "
"membandingkan data di beberapa kategori."

#: ../../content/applications/services/helpdesk/overview/sla.rst:190
msgid "Line Chart"
msgstr "Grafik Garis"

#: ../../content/applications/services/helpdesk/overview/sla.rst:0
msgid "View of the SLA status analysis report in line view."
msgstr "Tampilan laporan analisis status SLA dalam tampilan garis."

#: ../../content/applications/services/helpdesk/overview/sla.rst:196
msgid "A line chart can visualize data trends or changes over time."
msgstr ""
"Grafik garis dapat memvisualisasikan tren data atau perubahan dari waktu ke "
"waktu."

#: ../../content/applications/services/helpdesk/overview/sla.rst:198
msgid "Pie Chart"
msgstr "Grafik Pie"

#: ../../content/applications/services/helpdesk/overview/sla.rst:0
msgid "View of the SLA status analysis report in pie chart view."
msgstr "Tampilan laporan analisis status SLA dalam tampilan diagram lingkaran."

#: ../../content/applications/services/helpdesk/overview/sla.rst:204
msgid "A pie chart compares data among a small number of categories."
msgstr "Diagram pai membandingkan data di antara sejumlah kecil kategori."

#: ../../content/applications/services/helpdesk/overview/sla.rst:207
msgid ""
"Both the :guilabel:`Bar Chart` and :guilabel:`Line Chart` views can "
"be :guilabel:`Stacked` by selecting the :guilabel:`Stacked` icon. This "
"displays two or more groups on top of each other instead of next to each "
"other, making it easier to compare data."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/services/helpdesk/overview/sla.rst:0
msgid "View of the SLA status analysis report in bar view, stacked."
msgstr "Tampilan laporan analisis status SLA dalam tampilan batang, bertumpuk."

#: ../../content/applications/services/helpdesk/overview/sla.rst:216
msgid "Cohort view"
msgstr "Tampilan cohort"

#: ../../content/applications/services/helpdesk/overview/sla.rst:218
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Cohort` view is used to track the changes in data over a "
"period of time. To display the :guilabel:`SLA Status Analysis` report in "
"a :guilabel:`Cohort` view, click the :guilabel:`Cohort` button, represented "
"by :guilabel:`(four cascading horizontal lines)`, in the top-right corner, "
"next to the other view options."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/services/helpdesk/overview/sla.rst:227
msgid "View of the SLA status analysis report in cohort view."
msgstr "Tampilan laporan analisis status SLA dalam tampilan cohort."

#: ../../content/applications/services/helpdesk/overview/sla.rst:227
msgid "The cohort view examines the life cycle of data over time."
msgstr "Tampilan cohort memeriksa siklus hidup data dari waktu ke waktu."

#: ../../content/applications/services/helpdesk/overview/sla.rst:230
msgid ":ref:`Reporting views <reporting/views>`"
msgstr ":ref:`Tampilan pelaporan <reporting/views>`"

#: ../../content/applications/services/helpdesk/overview/sla.rst:231
msgid ""
":doc:`Allow customers to close their tickets </applications/services/"
"helpdesk/advanced/close_tickets>`"
msgstr ""
":doc:`Izinkan pelanggan untuk menutup tiket mereka </applications/services/"
"helpdesk/advanced/close_tickets>`"

#: ../../content/applications/services/planning.rst:5
msgid "Planning"
msgstr "Perencanaan"

#: ../../content/applications/services/planning.rst:7
msgid ""
"**Odoo Planning** allows you to plan your team's schedule and manage shifts "
"and resources."
msgstr ""
"**Odoo Planning** memungkinkan Anda merencanakan jadwal tim dan mengelola "
"shift serta sumber daya."

#: ../../content/applications/services/planning.rst:9
msgid ""
"Handling your team's planning comes with specific requirements that may vary "
"widely depending on your business needs. The following concepts were "
"introduced in Odoo Planning to meet those needs:"
msgstr ""
"Menangani perencanaan tim Anda datang dengan persyaratan spesifik yang dapat "
"bervariasi secara luas tergantung pada kebutuhan bisnis Anda. Konsep berikut "
"diperkenalkan di Odoo Planning untuk memenuhi kebutuhan tersebut:"

#: ../../content/applications/services/planning.rst:12
msgid ""
"**Shifts** are dispatched to **resources**, which can be either :ref:`human "
"<planning/employees>` (employees) or :ref:`material <planning/materials>` "
"(e.g., equipment). The resources are assigned :ref:`roles <planning/roles>`, "
"which allows for organization of work within the team."
msgstr ""
"**Shift** didistribusikan ke **sumber daya**, yang dapat berupa "
":ref:`manusia <planning/employees>` (karyawan) atau :ref:`material <planning/"
"materials>` (misalnya, peralatan). Sumber daya tersebut ditugaskan "
":ref:`peran <planning/roles>`, yang memungkinkan pengorganisasian pekerjaan "
"dalam tim."

#: ../../content/applications/services/planning.rst:16
msgid ""
"Once the initial configuration is done, :ref:`planning shifts <planning/"
"shifts>` can be done manually or automated by using the :ref:`Auto Plan "
"<planning/open-shifts>` feature."
msgstr ""
"Setelah konfigurasi awal selesai, :ref:`perencanaan shift <planning/shifts>` "
"dapat dilakukan secara manual atau otomatis dengan menggunakan fitur "
":ref:`Rencanakan Otomatis <planning/open-shifts>`."

#: ../../content/applications/services/planning.rst:19
msgid ""
"An integration between the Planning and Sales apps allows the linking of "
"sold services to roles and shifts in Planning. Additionally, integration "
"with :doc:`Project <project>` allows dedicating shifts, and thus time and "
"resources, to specific projects."
msgstr ""
"Integrasi antara aplikasi Perencanaan dan Penjualan memungkinkan pengaitan "
"layanan yang dijual dengan peran dan shift di Perencanaan. Selain itu, "
"integrasi dengan :doc:`Project <project>` memungkinkan dedikasi shift, dan "
"dengan demikian waktu dan sumber daya, untuk proyek tertentu."

#: ../../content/applications/services/planning.rst:24
msgid "`Odoo tutorials: Planning <https://www.odoo.com/slides/planning-60>`_"
msgstr "`Tutorial Odoo: Planning <https://www.odoo.com/slides/planning-60>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/services/planning.rst:34
msgid "Roles"
msgstr "Peran-Peran"

#: ../../content/applications/services/planning.rst:36
msgid ""
"To define the roles your resources perform (e.g., chef, bartender, waiter), "
"go to :menuselection:`Planning --> Configuration --> Roles`, then "
"click :guilabel:`New`, and fill in the :guilabel:`Name` (e.g., assistant, "
"receptionist, manager). Then, choose the :guilabel:`Resources` that will "
"perform this role. Resources can be either :ref:`Employees <planning/"
"employees>` or :ref:`Materials <planning/materials>`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menentukan peran yang dilakukan sumber daya Anda (misalnya, koki, "
"bartender, pelayan), buka :menuselection:`Perencanaan --> Konfigurasi --> "
"Peran`, lalu klik :guilabel:`Baru`, dan isi :guilabel:`Nama` (misalnya, "
"asisten, resepsionis, manajer). Kemudian, pilih :guilabel:`Sumber Daya` yang "
"akan menjalankan peran ini. Sumber daya dapat berupa :ref:`Karyawan "
"<planning/employees>` atau :ref:`Material <planning/materials>`."

#: ../../content/applications/services/planning.rst:43
msgid ""
"If the Sales app is installed in your database, the :guilabel:`Services` "
"field appears, allowing you to specify which roles are needed to perform "
"services so that the shifts are dispatched to the right person."
msgstr ""
"Jika aplikasi Penjualan diinstal di database Anda, bidang "
":guilabel:`Layanan` muncul, memungkinkan Anda menentukan peran mana yang "
"diperlukan untuk melakukan layanan sehingga shift didistribusikan ke orang "
"yang tepat."

#: ../../content/applications/services/planning.rst:46
msgid ""
"Roles are taken into account when using the :ref:`Auto Plan feature "
"<planning/open-shifts>`."
msgstr ""
"Peran diperhitungkan saat menggunakan :ref:`fitur Rencanakan Otomatis "
"<planning/open-shifts>`."

#: ../../content/applications/services/planning.rst:49
msgid "Property fields and roles"
msgstr "Bidang properti dan peran"

#: ../../content/applications/services/planning.rst:51
msgid ""
"**Property fields** allow you to add custom fields to forms across several "
"Odoo applications. Planning includes the possibility of adding property "
"fields linked to roles to shifts."
msgstr ""
"**Bidang properti** memungkinkan Anda menambahkan bidang khusus ke formulir "
"di berbagai aplikasi Odoo. Perencanaan mencakup kemungkinan menambahkan "
"bidang properti yang terkait dengan peran ke shift."

#: ../../content/applications/services/planning.rst:54
msgid ""
"To create a property field, switch to the list view from any schedule. From "
"there, click :guilabel:`View` on the shift that you wish to edit. If "
"the :guilabel:`Role` field is empty, fill it in with the desired role, then "
"click the cog icon and select :guilabel:`Add Properties`. :doc:`Configure "
"<../productivity/knowledge/properties>` the new field according to your "
"needs."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/services/planning.rst:None
msgid "Creating a new property field in Planning."
msgstr "Membuat field properti baru di Perencanaan."

#: ../../content/applications/services/planning.rst:62
msgid ""
"The property field is linked to the role and is included in the shift form "
"of all shifts performed by this role."
msgstr ""
"Field properti terhubung ke peran dan disertakan dalam formulir shift semua "
"shift yang dilakukan oleh peran ini."

#: ../../content/applications/services/planning.rst:66
msgid "Some of the use cases of role property fields include:"
msgstr "Beberapa kasus penggunaan field properti peran meliputi:"

#: ../../content/applications/services/planning.rst:68
msgid ""
"**Accreditation**: for roles that require a specific permit (e.g., driving "
"license)"
msgstr "**Akreditasi**: untuk peran yang memerlukan izin khusus (misalnya, SIM)"

#: ../../content/applications/services/planning.rst:69
msgid ""
"**Location**: in companies that operate in multiple locations (e.g., shops "
"or restaurants)"
msgstr ""
"**Lokasi**: di perusahaan yang beroperasi di beberapa lokasi (misalnya, toko "
"atau restoran)"

#: ../../content/applications/services/planning.rst:70
msgid "**Language**: in a multi-lingual environment (e.g., consulting company)"
msgstr "**Bahasa**: di lingkungan multibahasa (misalnya, perusahaan konsultan)"

#: ../../content/applications/services/planning.rst:75
msgid "Employees"
msgstr "Karyawan"

#: ../../content/applications/services/planning.rst:77
msgid "All employees can be included in the planning and assigned shifts."
msgstr "Semua karyawan dapat disertakan dalam perencanaan dan diberi shift."

#: ../../content/applications/services/planning.rst:79
msgid ""
"To adapt the employee's planning settings, go to :menuselection:`Planning --"
"> Configuration --> Employees`, and choose the employee for whom you want to "
"edit the settings. Then, go to the :guilabel:`Work Information` tab."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menyesuaikan pengaturan perencanaan karyawan, buka "
":menuselection:`Perencanaan --> Configuration --> Employees`, dan pilih "
"karyawan yang ingin Anda edit pengaturannya. Kemudian, buka tab "
":guilabel:`Work Information`."

#: ../../content/applications/services/planning.rst:None
msgid "Employee profile and the work information tab."
msgstr "Profil karyawan dan tab informasi kerja."

#: ../../content/applications/services/planning.rst:87
msgid ""
"You can do the same from the **Employees** app, which is installed by "
"default along with Planning."
msgstr ""
"Anda dapat melakukan hal yang sama dari aplikasi **Karyawan**, yang diinstal "
"secara default bersama dengan Perencanaan."

#: ../../content/applications/services/planning.rst:90
msgid ""
"Two sections of the employee's :guilabel:`Work Information` tab have an "
"impact on Planning: :guilabel:`Schedule` (namely, the :guilabel:`Working "
"Hours` field) and :guilabel:`Planning`."
msgstr ""
"Dua bagian dari tab :guilabel:`Work Information` karyawan berdampak pada "
"Perencanaan: :guilabel:`Schedule` (yaitu, field :guilabel:`Working Hours`) "
"dan :guilabel:`Planning`."

#: ../../content/applications/services/planning.rst:96
msgid "Working hours"
msgstr "Jam kerja"

#: ../../content/applications/services/planning.rst:98
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Working Hours` are taken into account when "
"the :guilabel:`Allocated Time` and its percentage is calculated "
"for :ref:`shifts <planning/templates>`. If the :guilabel:`Working Hours` "
"field is left blank, the employee is considered to be working flexible hours."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Working Hours` diperhitungkan ketika :guilabel:`Allocated Time` "
"dan persentasenya dihitung untuk :ref:`shift <planning/templates>`. Jika "
"field :guilabel:`Working Hours` dibiarkan kosong, karyawan dianggap bekerja "
"dengan jam fleksibel."

#: ../../content/applications/services/planning.rst:102
msgid ""
"To create individual :guilabel:`Working Hours`, for example, for employees "
"working part-time, click :guilabel:`Search more...`, then :guilabel:`New`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk membuat :guilabel:`Working Hours` individual, misalnya, untuk karyawan "
"yang bekerja paruh waktu, klik :guilabel:`Search more...`, lalu "
":guilabel:`New`."

#: ../../content/applications/services/planning.rst:106
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Working Hours` and the :guilabel:`Allocated Time` in Planning "
"can impact **Payroll**, if the employee's contract is configured to generate "
"work entries based on shifts."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Working Hours` dan :guilabel:`Allocated Time` di Perencanaan "
"dapat memengaruhi **Payroll**, jika kontrak karyawan dikonfigurasi untuk "
"menghasilkan entri kerja berdasarkan shift."

#: ../../content/applications/services/planning.rst:110
msgid ""
":ref:`Payroll documentation on working schedules <payroll/working-times>`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/services/planning.rst:113
msgid "Planning roles"
msgstr "Peran perencanaan"

#: ../../content/applications/services/planning.rst:115
msgid "Once an employee has one or more :guilabel:`Roles`:"
msgstr "Setelah seorang karyawan memiliki satu atau lebih :guilabel:`Roles`:"

#: ../../content/applications/services/planning.rst:117
msgid ""
"When creating a shift for this employee, only the shift templates from the "
"roles chosen in this field are displayed."
msgstr ""
"Saat membuat shift untuk karyawan ini, hanya template shift dari peran yang "
"dipilih di field ini yang ditampilkan."

#: ../../content/applications/services/planning.rst:119
msgid ""
"When a schedule is published, the employee is only notified of open shifts "
"for the roles that are assigned to them."
msgstr ""
"Ketika jadwal dipublikasikan, karyawan hanya diberitahu tentang shift "
"terbuka untuk peran yang ditetapkan kepada mereka."

#: ../../content/applications/services/planning.rst:121
msgid ""
"When auto-assigning open shifts or planning sales orders, the employee is "
"only assigned shifts for the roles assigned to them."
msgstr ""
"Saat menetapkan shift terbuka secara otomatis atau merencanakan sales order, "
"karyawan hanya diberi shift untuk peran yang ditetapkan kepada mereka."

#: ../../content/applications/services/planning.rst:124
msgid "Additionally, when a :guilabel:`Default role` is defined:"
msgstr "Selain itu, ketika :guilabel:`Peran default` didefinisikan:"

#: ../../content/applications/services/planning.rst:126
msgid ""
"When creating a shift for the employee, the default role is automatically "
"selected."
msgstr ""
"Saat membuat shift untuk karyawan, peran default dipilih secara otomatis."

#: ../../content/applications/services/planning.rst:127
msgid ""
"This role also has precedence over the other roles of the employee when auto-"
"assigning open shifts or planning sales orders."
msgstr ""
"Peran ini juga memiliki prioritas atas peran lain dari karyawan saat "
"menetapkan shift terbuka secara otomatis atau merencanakan sales order."

#: ../../content/applications/services/planning.rst:131
msgid ""
"If the Planning roles fields are left empty, there are no restrictions in "
"the shift templates and open shifts shared with the employee. However, it’s "
"not possible to use the **Auto Plan** feature for employee with no roles."
msgstr ""
"Jika kolom peran Perencanaan dibiarkan kosong, tidak ada batasan dalam "
"templat shift dan shift terbuka yang dibagikan dengan karyawan. Namun, tidak "
"mungkin menggunakan fitur **Rencanakan Otomatis** untuk karyawan tanpa peran."

#: ../../content/applications/services/planning.rst:138
msgid "Materials"
msgstr "Material"

#: ../../content/applications/services/planning.rst:140
msgid ""
"**Materials** are resources that can be assigned shifts and working hours "
"but are not employees. For example, a construction company could use "
"materials to create shifts for shared machines (e.g., cranes, forklifts)."
msgstr ""
"**Material** adalah sumber daya yang dapat diberi shift dan jam kerja tetapi "
"bukan karyawan. Misalnya, perusahaan konstruksi dapat menggunakan material "
"untuk membuat shift untuk mesin bersama (misalnya, derek, forklift)."

#: ../../content/applications/services/planning.rst:144
msgid ""
"Similarly to employees, materials can be assigned roles and working time."
msgstr "Sama seperti karyawan, material dapat diberi peran dan waktu kerja."

#: ../../content/applications/services/planning.rst:149
msgid "Shift templates"
msgstr "Template shift"

#: ../../content/applications/services/planning.rst:151
msgid ""
"To create a shift template, click :guilabel:`New` on any schedule, then fill "
"in the :ref:`details of the shift <planning/create-shift>`. In order for the "
"shift to be saved as a template, tick :guilabel:`Save as Template`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/services/planning.rst:None
msgid "Shift form with the option `save template` ticked."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/services/planning.rst:158
msgid ""
"Alternatively, you can go to :menuselection:`Planning --> Configuration --> "
"Shift Templates`, then click :guilabel:`New`. Fill in the :guilabel:`Start "
"Hour` and :guilabel:`Shift Duration`. The shift’s :guilabel:`End Time` is "
"then calculated based on the :guilabel:`Working Hours`, taking into account "
"working time as well as breaks."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/services/planning.rst:164
msgid ""
"The employee's working hours are Monday to Friday, 8 am to 5 pm, with a "
"break between 12 and 1 pm."
msgstr ""
"Jam kerja karyawan adalah Senin hingga Jumat, pukul 8 pagi hingga 5 sore, "
"dengan istirahat antara pukul 12 dan 1 siang."

#: ../../content/applications/services/planning.rst:167
msgid ""
"Creating a shift template with a start hour of 9 am and a duration of 8 "
"hours will result in the end hour being 5 pm, based on the working hours and "
"the 1-hour break."
msgstr ""
"Membuat templat shift dengan jam mulai pukul 9 pagi dan durasi 8 jam akan "
"menghasilkan jam selesai pukul 5 sore, berdasarkan jam kerja dan istirahat 1 "
"jam."

#: ../../content/applications/services/planning.rst:169
msgid ""
"Creating a shift template with a start hour of 10 am and a duration of 10 "
"hours will result in the end hour of 10 am the following day, as the company "
"is closed at 5 pm according to the working hours."
msgstr ""
"Membuat templat shift dengan jam mulai pukul 10 pagi dan durasi 10 jam akan "
"menghasilkan jam selesai pukul 10 pagi keesokan harinya, karena perusahaan "
"tutup pada pukul 5 sore sesuai jam kerja."

#: ../../content/applications/services/planning.rst:173
msgid "Additionally, for each shift template, you can also configure:"
msgstr "Selain itu, untuk setiap templat shift, Anda juga dapat mengonfigurasi:"

#: ../../content/applications/services/planning.rst:175
msgid ":guilabel:`Role`: to link the shift to this specific role."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Peran`: untuk menghubungkan shift dengan peran spesifik ini."

#: ../../content/applications/services/planning.rst:176
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Project`: to keep track of shifts that are dedicated to work on a "
"project."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Project`: untuk melacak shift yang didedikasikan untuk pekerjaan "
"pada project."

#: ../../content/applications/services/planning.rst:181
msgid "Planning shifts"
msgstr "Merencanakan shift"

#: ../../content/applications/services/planning.rst:183
msgid ""
"On opening the Planning app, the users see their own schedule. Users with "
"admin roles can also see :guilabel:`Schedule by "
"Resource`, :guilabel:`Role`, :guilabel:`Project`, or :guilabel:`Sales "
"Order`, as well as reporting and configuration menus."
msgstr ""
"Saat membuka aplikasi Perencanaan, pengguna melihat jadwal mereka sendiri. "
"Pengguna dengan peran admin juga dapat melihat :guilabel:`Jadwal berdasarkan "
"Sumber Daya`, :guilabel:`Peran`, :guilabel:`Project`, atau :guilabel:`Sales "
"Order`, serta menu pelaporan dan konfigurasi."

#: ../../content/applications/services/planning.rst:188
msgid ""
"The schedule is displayed in the Gantt view, which allows you to edit (with "
"a drag and drop), resize, split, and duplicate shifts without having to open "
"them."
msgstr ""
"Jadwal ditampilkan dalam tampilan Gantt, yang memungkinkan Anda mengedit "
"(dengan seret dan lepas), mengubah ukuran, membagi, dan menduplikasi shift "
"tanpa harus membukanya."

#: ../../content/applications/services/planning.rst:None
msgid "A schedule displaying various visual elements."
msgstr "Jadwal yang menampilkan berbagai elemen visual."

#: ../../content/applications/services/planning.rst:194
msgid "The following visual elements are used on the shifts in the schedules:"
msgstr "Elemen visual berikut digunakan pada shift dalam jadwal:"

#: ../../content/applications/services/planning.rst:196
msgid "**Full color**: shifts that are planned and published."
msgstr "**Warna penuh**: shift yang direncanakan dan dipublikasikan."

#: ../../content/applications/services/planning.rst:197
msgid ""
"**Diagonal stripes**: shifts that are planned but have yet to be published."
msgstr ""
"**Garis diagonal**: shift yang direncanakan tetapi belum dipublikasikan."

#: ../../content/applications/services/planning.rst:198
msgid "**Grayed-out background**: employees that are on time off."
msgstr "**Latar belakang abu-abu**: karyawan yang sedang cuti."

#: ../../content/applications/services/planning.rst:199
msgid ""
"**Progress bar**: currently ongoing shifts with timesheets linked to them."
msgstr ""
"**Progress bar**: shift yang sedang berlangsung dengan tabel waktu yang "
"terhubung dengannya."

#: ../../content/applications/services/planning.rst:200
msgid ""
"**Grayed-out shift**: when copying shifts, the copied shifts are shown in "
"full color, whereas previously existing shifts are temporarily greyed out. "
"The color changes back to full color or diagonal stripes on the next refresh "
"of the page or by removing the filter."
msgstr ""
"**Shift abu-abu**: saat menyalin shift, shift yang disalin ditampilkan "
"dengan warna penuh, sedangkan shift yang sudah ada sebelumnya ditampilkan "
"sementara dengan warna abu-abu. Warna berubah kembali ke warna penuh atau "
"garis diagonal pada penyegaran halaman berikutnya atau dengan menghapus "
"filter."

#: ../../content/applications/services/planning.rst:207
msgid "Create a shift"
msgstr "Membuat shift"

#: ../../content/applications/services/planning.rst:209
msgid ""
"To create a shift, go to any schedule, then click :guilabel:`New`. In the "
"pop-up window that opens, fill in the following details:"
msgstr ""
"Untuk membuat shift, buka jadwal mana pun, lalu klik :guilabel:`New`. Pada "
"jendela pop-up yang terbuka, isi detail berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/services/planning.rst:212
msgid ""
"**Templates**: If there is one or more templates existing in your database, "
"they are displayed in the upper section of the pop-up window. Once selected, "
"a template prefills the shift form accordingly."
msgstr ""
"**Templates**: Jika ada satu atau lebih template yang ada di database Anda, "
"template tersebut ditampilkan di bagian atas jendela pop-up. Setelah "
"dipilih, template akan mengisi formulir shift secara otomatis."

#: ../../content/applications/services/planning.rst:215
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Resource`: Resources can be both employees or materials. If this "
"field is left empty, the shift is considered an :ref:`open shift <planning/"
"open-shifts>`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Resource`: Resource dapat berupa karyawan atau material. Jika "
"field ini dibiarkan kosong, shift tersebut dianggap sebagai :ref:`open shift "
"<planning/open-shifts>`."

#: ../../content/applications/services/planning.rst:217
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Role`: Select the role that the resource assigned will be "
"performing. This field is used when :ref:`auto-planning <planning/open-"
"shifts>` shifts. Once you select a role, the shift templates associated with "
"it are displayed in the upper section of the pop-up window."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Role`: Pilih peran yang akan dilakukan oleh resource yang "
"ditugaskan. Field ini digunakan saat :ref:`auto-planning <planning/open-"
"shifts>` shift. Setelah Anda memilih peran, template shift yang terkait "
"dengannya ditampilkan di bagian atas jendela pop-up."

#: ../../content/applications/services/planning.rst:220
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Project`: If the Project app is installed in your database, this "
"field allows you to link the project to the shift is available, allowing you "
"to plan and track shifts dedicated to work on the selected project."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Project`: Jika aplikasi Project diinstal di database Anda, field "
"ini memungkinkan Anda menghubungkan project ke shift yang tersedia, "
"memungkinkan Anda merencanakan dan melacak shift yang didedikasikan untuk "
"bekerja pada project yang dipilih."

#: ../../content/applications/services/planning.rst:223
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Sales Order Item`: If the Sales app is installed in your "
"database, this field allows you to link a sales order to the shift."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Sales Order Item`: Jika aplikasi Penjualan diinstal di database "
"Anda, field ini memungkinkan Anda menghubungkan sales order ke shift."

#: ../../content/applications/services/planning.rst:225
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Repeat`: Tick the checkbox and configure the :guilabel:`Repeat "
"Every` field according to your needs. The following rules apply to recurring "
"shifts:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/services/planning.rst:228
msgid ""
"All fields "
"(e.g., :guilabel:`Resource`, :guilabel:`Role`, :guilabel:`Project`) are "
"copied from the original shift except for the date, which is adjusted "
"according to the :guilabel:`Repeat Every` field."
msgstr ""
"Semua field (misalnya :guilabel:`Resource`, :guilabel:`Role`, "
":guilabel:`Project`) disalin dari shift asli kecuali tanggal, yang "
"disesuaikan menurut field :guilabel:`Repeat Every`."

#: ../../content/applications/services/planning.rst:231
msgid "Recurrences are planned but not published."
msgstr "Pengulangan direncanakan tetapi tidak dipublikasikan."

#: ../../content/applications/services/planning.rst:232
msgid ""
"By default, planned shifts are created six months in advance, after which "
"they are created gradually. To change the time frame, :ref:`activate the "
"Developer mode <developer-mode>`, then go to :menuselection:`Planning --> "
"Configuration --> Settings` and edit the :guilabel:`Recurring Shifts`."
msgstr ""
"Secara default, shift yang direncanakan dibuat enam bulan sebelumnya, "
"setelah itu dibuat secara bertahap. Untuk mengubah kerangka waktu, "
":ref:`aktifkan mode pengembang <developer-mode>`, lalu buka "
":menuselection:`Planning --> Configuration --> Settings` dan edit "
":guilabel:`Recurring Shifts`."

#: ../../content/applications/services/planning.rst:237
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Save as Template`: When this option is ticked, a shift template "
"is created with the same :guilabel:`Start and End "
"hours`, :guilabel:`Allocated time`, :guilabel:`Role`, "
"and :guilabel:`Project`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/services/planning.rst:240
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Additional note sent to the employee`: Click on the field to add "
"a note."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Additional note sent to the employee`: Klik field untuk "
"menambahkan catatan."

#: ../../content/applications/services/planning.rst:241
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Date`: Choose the date and time of your shift. This is the only "
"mandatory field when creating a shift."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Date`: Pilih tanggal dan waktu shift Anda. Ini adalah satu-"
"satunya field wajib saat membuat shift."

#: ../../content/applications/services/planning.rst:243
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Allocated time`: Is calculated based on the date and the "
"employee’s :guilabel:`Working Schedule`. See more in :ref:`Shift Templates "
"<planning/templates>`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Allocated time`: Dihitung berdasarkan tanggal dan "
":guilabel:`Working Schedule` karyawan. Lihat lebih lanjut di :ref:`Shift "
"Templates <planning/templates>`."

#: ../../content/applications/services/planning.rst:246
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Publish & Save` to confirm the shift and send the assigned "
"employee their schedule by email."
msgstr ""
"Klik :guilabel:`Publish & Save` untuk mengonfirmasi shift dan mengirim "
"jadwal kepada karyawan yang ditugaskan melalui email."

#: ../../content/applications/services/planning.rst:250
msgid ""
"The draft is visible on the admin planning view and can be identified by "
"diagonal lines. The employee is only notified of the shift once it's "
"published."
msgstr ""
"Draf terlihat di tampilan perencanaan admin dan dapat diidentifikasi dengan "
"garis diagonal. Karyawan hanya diberi tahu tentang shift setelah "
"dipublikasikan."

#: ../../content/applications/services/planning.rst:253
msgid ""
"Two kinds of notifications are sent to the employees depending on their "
"account configuration:"
msgstr ""
"Dua jenis notifikasi dikirim kepada karyawan tergantung pada konfigurasi "
"akun mereka:"

#: ../../content/applications/services/planning.rst:255
msgid ""
"Employees without user accounts are redirected to a dedicated **Planning "
"portal**."
msgstr "Karyawan tanpa akun user dialihkan ke **portal Perencanaan** khusus."

#: ../../content/applications/services/planning.rst:256
msgid ""
"Employees with a user account are redirected to the :guilabel:`My Planning` "
"view in the backend view of Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Karyawan dengan akun user dialihkan ke tampilan :guilabel:`Perencanaan Saya` "
"di tampilan backend Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/services/planning.rst:260
msgid ""
"The **split shifts** tool allows to easily split a long shift into segments. "
"To do so, hover the mouse over the desired shift and click the :icon:`fa-"
"scissors` (:guilabel:`scissors`) icon."
msgstr ""
"Alat **pembagian shift** memungkinkan pembagian shift panjang menjadi "
"beberapa segmen dengan mudah. Untuk melakukannya, arahkan kursor ke shift "
"yang diinginkan dan klik ikon :icon:`fa-scissors` (:guilabel:`gunting`)."

#: ../../content/applications/services/planning.rst:0
msgid "Split shifts tool."
msgstr "Alat pembagian shift."

#: ../../content/applications/services/planning.rst:269
msgid "Open shifts and auto planning"
msgstr "Shift terbuka dan perencanaan otomatis"

#: ../../content/applications/services/planning.rst:271
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Auto Plan` button allows you to assign **Open shifts** "
"(shifts with no resource assigned) and create and assign shifts linked to "
"sales orders or project."
msgstr ""
"Tombol :guilabel:`Rencanakan Otomatis` memungkinkan Anda menugaskan **Shift "
"terbuka** (shift tanpa sumber daya yang ditugaskan) dan membuat serta "
"menugaskan shift yang terkait dengan pesanan penjualan atau project."

#: ../../content/applications/services/planning.rst:274
msgid "The following features have an impact on auto planning:"
msgstr "Fitur-fitur berikut berdampak pada perencanaan otomatis:"

#: ../../content/applications/services/planning.rst:276
msgid ""
"**Roles**: Open shifts are only assigned to resources (employees or "
"materials) that have the corresponding role assigned. It is not possible to "
"use the :guilabel:`Auto Plan` feature for employee with no roles."
msgstr ""
"**Peran**: Shift terbuka hanya ditugaskan ke sumber daya (karyawan atau "
"material) yang memiliki peran yang sesuai. Tidak mungkin menggunakan fitur "
":guilabel:`Rencanakan Otomatis` untuk karyawan tanpa peran."

#: ../../content/applications/services/planning.rst:279
msgid ""
"**Default roles**: The default role assigned to a resource is given priority "
"over the other roles they have assigned to them."
msgstr ""
"**Peran default**: Peran default yang ditugaskan ke sumber daya "
"diprioritaskan di atas peran lain yang mereka miliki."

#: ../../content/applications/services/planning.rst:281
msgid ""
"**Conflicts**: Employees or materials cannot be assigned multiple shifts at "
"the same time."
msgstr ""
"**Konflik**: Karyawan atau material tidak dapat ditugaskan beberapa shift "
"pada waktu yang sama."

#: ../../content/applications/services/planning.rst:282
msgid ""
"**Time off**: The employees’ time off is taken into account, as well as "
"public holidays."
msgstr "**Cuti**: Cuti karyawan diperhitungkan, termasuk hari libur nasional."

#: ../../content/applications/services/planning.rst:283
msgid ""
"**Working hours**: Are taken into account when assigning shifts to employees "
"or materials. It is not possible to use the :guilabel:`Auto Plan` feature "
"for an employee who is working :ref:`flexible hours <planning/working-"
"hours>`."
msgstr ""
"**Jam kerja**: Diperhitungkan saat menugaskan shift ke karyawan atau "
"material. Tidak mungkin menggunakan fitur :guilabel:`Rencanakan Otomatis` "
"untuk karyawan yang bekerja dengan :ref:`jam fleksibel <planning/working-"
"hours>`."

#: ../../content/applications/services/planning.rst:286
msgid ""
"**Contracts**: If the employee has an active contract, they won't be "
"assigned shifts that fall outside of their contract period."
msgstr ""
"**Kontrak**: Jika karyawan memiliki kontrak aktif, mereka tidak akan "
"ditugaskan shift yang berada di luar periode kontrak mereka."

#: ../../content/applications/services/planning.rst:289
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Publish` to confirm the schedule and notify the employees "
"of their planning."
msgstr ""
"Klik :guilabel:`Publikasikan` untuk mengonfirmasi jadwal dan memberi "
"notifikasi kepada karyawan tentang perencanaan mereka."

#: ../../content/applications/services/planning.rst:294
msgid "Switching shifts and unassignment"
msgstr "Pertukaran shift dan pembatalan penugasan"

#: ../../content/applications/services/planning.rst:296
msgid ""
"Two features are available to allow employees to make changes to their "
"schedule: **switching shifts** and **unassignment**."
msgstr ""
"Dua fitur tersedia untuk memungkinkan karyawan melakukan perubahan pada "
"jadwal mereka: **pertukaran shift** dan **pembatalan penugasan**."

#: ../../content/applications/services/planning.rst:300
msgid ""
"These features are mutually exclusive. Switching shifts is possible by "
"default and cannot be disabled. However, once the **Allow unassignment** "
"feature is enabled, it replaces the option to switch shifts."
msgstr ""
"Kedua fitur ini saling eksklusif. Pertukaran shift dimungkinkan secara "
"default dan tidak dapat dinonaktifkan. Namun, setelah fitur **Izinkan "
"pembatalan penugasan** diaktifkan, fitur ini menggantikan opsi untuk menukar "
"shift."

#: ../../content/applications/services/planning.rst:305
msgid "Switching shifts"
msgstr "Mengganti shift"

#: ../../content/applications/services/planning.rst:307
msgid ""
"Once shifts are planned and published, employees receive an email "
"notification. If an employee wishes to switch a shift, they can click the "
"unwanted shift and click :guilabel:`Ask to switch`."
msgstr ""
"Setelah shift direncanakan dan dipublikasikan, karyawan menerima notifikasi "
"email. Jika seorang karyawan ingin menukar shift, mereka dapat mengklik "
"shift yang tidak diinginkan dan klik :guilabel:`Minta untuk menukar`."

#: ../../content/applications/services/planning.rst:310
msgid ""
"The shift remains assigned to the original employee, but in the schedule, a "
"notification informing that the assigned employee would like to switch "
"shifts is visible on the shift."
msgstr ""
"Shift tetap ditugaskan ke karyawan awal, tetapi dalam jadwal, notifikasi "
"yang menginformasikan bahwa karyawan yang ditugaskan ingin menukar shift "
"terlihat pada shift tersebut."

#: ../../content/applications/services/planning.rst:313
msgid ""
"The shift is then displayed to other employees who share the same role, and "
"if they wish to assign it to themselves, they can click the :guilabel:`I "
"take it` button."
msgstr ""
"Shift kemudian ditampilkan kepada karyawan lain yang memiliki peran yang "
"sama, dan jika mereka ingin menugaskannya ke diri mereka sendiri, mereka "
"dapat mengklik tombol :guilabel:`Saya ambil`."

#: ../../content/applications/services/planning.rst:317
#: ../../content/applications/services/planning.rst:335
msgid "The following rules apply:"
msgstr "Aturan berikut berlaku:"

#: ../../content/applications/services/planning.rst:319
msgid ""
"Only the shifts matching the employee's roles are displayed as available to "
"them."
msgstr ""
"Hanya shift yang cocok dengan peran karyawan yang ditampilkan sebagai "
"tersedia untuk mereka."

#: ../../content/applications/services/planning.rst:320
msgid "Switching shifts is not available for shifts in the past."
msgstr "Pertukaran shift tidak tersedia untuk shift di masa lalu."

#: ../../content/applications/services/planning.rst:323
msgid "Unassignment"
msgstr "Pembatalan Penugasan"

#: ../../content/applications/services/planning.rst:325
msgid ""
"To allow employees to unassign themselves from shifts, go "
"to :menuselection:`Planning --> Configuration --> Settings`, then tick the "
"checkbox :guilabel:`Allow Unassignment`. Then, specify the maximum number of "
"days that the employees can unassign themselves before the shift."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengizinkan karyawan membatalkan penugasan mereka sendiri dari shift, "
"buka :menuselection:`Perencanaan --> Configuration --> Settings`, kemudian "
"centang kotak :guilabel:`Allow Unassignment`. Kemudian, tentukan jumlah "
"maksimum hari bahwa karyawan dapat membatalkan penugasan mereka sendiri "
"sebelum shift."

#: ../../content/applications/services/planning.rst:330
msgid ""
"Once shifts are planned and published, employees receive an email "
"notification. If shift unassignment is allowed, the employees can click "
"the :guilabel:`I am unavailable` button, and the shift reverts to an open "
"shift."
msgstr ""
"Setelah shift direncanakan dan dipublikasikan, karyawan menerima notifikasi "
"email. Jika pembatalan penugasan shift diizinkan, karyawan dapat mengklik "
"tombol :guilabel:`I am unavailable`, dan shift kembali menjadi shift terbuka."

#: ../../content/applications/services/planning.rst:337
msgid ""
"Only the shifts matching the employee's roles are displayed in their "
"schedule."
msgstr ""
"Hanya shift yang cocok dengan peran karyawan yang ditampilkan dalam jadwal "
"mereka."

#: ../../content/applications/services/planning.rst:338
msgid "Unassigning shifts is not available for shifts in the past."
msgstr "Pembatalan penugasan shift tidak tersedia untuk shift di masa lalu."

#: ../../content/applications/services/project.rst:8
msgid "Project"
msgstr "Proyek"

#: ../../content/applications/services/project.rst:10
msgid ""
"Odoo Project is a tool to manage your ongoing projects. Schedule tasks, "
"assign activities to coworkers, and keep track of each project's "
"profitability."
msgstr ""
"Odoo Project adalah alat untuk mengelola proyek yang sedang berlangsung. "
"Jadwalkan tugas, tugaskan aktivitas kepada rekan kerja, dan lacak "
"profitabilitas setiap proyek."

#: ../../content/applications/services/project.rst:14
#: ../../content/applications/services/timesheets.rst:11
msgid ""
"`Odoo Tutorials: Project and Timesheets <https://www.odoo.com/slides/project-"
"and-timesheets-21>`_"
msgstr ""
"`Odoo Tutorials: Project and Timesheets <https://www.odoo.com/slides/project-"
"and-timesheets-21>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/services/project/project_dashboard.rst:3
msgid "Project dashboard"
msgstr "Dashboard project"

#: ../../content/applications/services/project/project_dashboard.rst:5
msgid ""
"The project dashboard allows you to get a comprehensive overview of your "
"project's status. It displays information such as the total number of tasks, "
"timesheets, and planned hours linked to the project, as well as detailed "
"information about project milestones and its costs and revenues. Within the "
"project dashboard, you can create :guilabel:`Project updates`, which allow "
"you to take a snapshot of the project's status at a certain point in time. "
"As such, it is a crucial tool for effective project management and ensuring "
"that your project stays on track."
msgstr ""
"Dashboard project memungkinkan Anda mendapatkan gambaran menyeluruh tentang "
"status project Anda. Dashboard ini menampilkan informasi seperti jumlah "
"total task, tabel waktu, dan jam yang direncanakan yang terkait dengan "
"project, serta informasi detail tentang milestone project dan biaya serta "
"pendapatannya. Di dalam dashboard project, Anda dapat membuat "
":guilabel:`Project updates`, yang memungkinkan Anda mengambil snapshot "
"status project pada waktu tertentu. Dengan demikian, ini adalah alat penting "
"untuk manajemen project yang efektif dan memastikan project Anda tetap pada "
"jalurnya."

#: ../../content/applications/services/project/project_dashboard.rst:13
msgid "Using the project dashboard"
msgstr "Menggunakan dashboard project"

#: ../../content/applications/services/project/project_dashboard.rst:15
msgid ""
"To access the project dashboard, open the **Project** app and hover over the "
"desired project’s card. Then, click the :icon:`fa-vertical-ellipsis` "
"(:guilabel:`vertical ellipsis`) icon and select :guilabel:`Dashboard`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/services/project/project_dashboard.rst:19
msgid ""
"The left side of the dashboard displays a list of existing :ref:`project "
"updates <project/project-dashboard/updates>`, and the right side "
"provides :ref:`detailed information about records linked to the project "
"<project/project-dashboard/smart-buttons>`, as well as :ref:`milestones "
"<project/project-dashboard/milestones>`, :ref:`profitability <project/"
"project-dashboard/profitability>`, and :ref:`budgets <project/project-"
"dashboard/budgets>`."
msgstr ""
"Sisi kiri dashboard menampilkan daftar :ref:`pembaruan project <project/"
"project-dashboard/updates>` yang ada, dan sisi kanan menyediakan "
":ref:`informasi detail tentang catatan yang terkait dengan project <project/"
"project-dashboard/smart-buttons>`, serta :ref:`milestone <project/project-"
"dashboard/milestones>`, :ref:`profitabilitas <project/project-dashboard/"
"profitability>`, dan :ref:`anggaran <project/project-dashboard/budgets>`."

#: ../../content/applications/services/project/project_dashboard.rst:26
msgid ""
"The information displayed on the project dashboard varies depending on the "
"applications installed on your database. For example, you will not see "
"information about **Timesheets**, **Planning**, or **Purchase Orders** if "
"the corresponding applications are not installed."
msgstr ""
"Informasi yang ditampilkan pada dashboard project bervariasi tergantung pada "
"aplikasi yang terpasang pada database Anda. Misalnya, Anda tidak akan "
"melihat informasi tentang **Tabel Waktu**, **Perencanaan**, atau **Purchase "
"Order** jika aplikasi yang sesuai tidak terpasang."

#: ../../content/applications/services/project/project_dashboard.rst:33
msgid "Totals smart buttons"
msgstr "Tombol pintar total"

#: ../../content/applications/services/project/project_dashboard.rst:35
msgid ""
"The following smart buttons are displayed on the top left of the project "
"dashboard:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/services/project/project_dashboard.rst:37
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Tasks`: the number of completed (i.e., :guilabel:`Done` "
"or :guilabel:`Canceled` :ref:`tasks <project/tasks/task_stages_statuses/"
"statuses>`) and all tasks, in format completed/all, as well as the entire "
"project's completion percentage estimation."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Tasks`: jumlah task yang selesai (yaitu, :guilabel:`Done` atau "
":guilabel:`Canceled` :ref:`task <project/tasks/task_stages_statuses/statuses>"
"`) dan semua task, dalam format selesai/semua, serta estimasi persentase "
"penyelesaian keseluruhan project."

#: ../../content/applications/services/project/project_dashboard.rst:40
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Timesheets`: the number of hours or days (depending on the "
"**Timesheets** app configuration) linked to the project. This includes "
"all :doc:`timesheets <../timesheets>`, whether or not they have been "
"validated."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/services/project/project_dashboard.rst:43
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Planned`: the number of hours that have been planned for shifts "
"in the **Planning** app. This includes all :doc:`planned shifts <../"
"planning>`, including past shifts and shifts that have not yet been "
"published."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/services/project/project_dashboard.rst:46
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Documents`: number of :doc:`documents <../../productivity/"
"documents>` in the project’s workspace."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/services/project/project_dashboard.rst:48
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Burndown Chart`: click the smart button to access a :doc:`report "
"</applications/essentials/reporting>` on the status of the project’s tasks "
"over time."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Burndown Chart`: klik tombol pintar untuk mengakses :doc:`laporan "
"</applications/essentials/reporting>` tentang status task project dari waktu "
"ke waktu."

#: ../../content/applications/services/project/project_dashboard.rst:50
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Timesheets and Planning`: click the smart button to access "
"a :doc:`report </applications/essentials/reporting>` on the project’s "
"timesheets and shifts."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/services/project/project_dashboard.rst:52
msgid ""
"**Additional fields**, such as :guilabel:`Sales Orders`, :guilabel:`Sales "
"Order Items`, :guilabel:`Purchase Orders`, and more, represent the number of "
"records linked to the project."
msgstr ""
"**Bidang tambahan**, seperti :guilabel:`Sales Orders`, :guilabel:`Sales "
"Order Items`, :guilabel:`Purchase Orders`, dan lainnya, mewakili jumlah "
"catatan yang terkait dengan project."

#: ../../content/applications/services/project/project_dashboard.rst:56
msgid ""
"Use the project dashboard smart buttons to update the project records "
"easily. Click :guilabel:`Timesheets` to validate "
"timesheets, :guilabel:`Planned` to create project "
"planning, :guilabel:`Documents` to view and validate documents, etc."
msgstr ""
"Gunakan tombol pintar dashboard project untuk memperbarui catatan project "
"dengan mudah. Klik :guilabel:`Timesheets` untuk memvalidasi tabel waktu, "
":guilabel:`Planned` untuk membuat perencanaan project, :guilabel:`Documents` "
"untuk melihat dan memvalidasi dokumen, dll."

#: ../../content/applications/services/project/project_dashboard.rst:63
msgid "Milestones"
msgstr "Milestone"

#: ../../content/applications/services/project/project_dashboard.rst:65
msgid ""
"This section is only visible if :doc:`milestones </applications/sales/sales/"
"invoicing/milestone>` have been created for this project. "
"Click :guilabel:`Add Milestone` to create a new milestone. Click a milestone "
"in the checklist to edit it, enable its checkbox to mark it as completed, or "
"click the :icon:`fa-trash` (:guilabel:`trash`) icon to remove it."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/services/project/project_dashboard.rst:73
msgid "Profitability"
msgstr "Profitabilitas"

#: ../../content/applications/services/project/project_dashboard.rst:75
msgid ""
"This section only applies to billable projects and provides a breakdown of "
"project costs and revenues."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/services/project/project_dashboard.rst:81
msgid "Budgets"
msgstr "Anggaran"

#: ../../content/applications/services/project/project_dashboard.rst:83
msgid ""
"If a budget has been set for the project, its status and related details are "
"displayed in this section. Click :guilabel:`Add Budget` to create a new "
"budget for the project."
msgstr ""
"Jika anggaran telah ditetapkan untuk proyek, statusnya dan detail terkait "
"ditampilkan di bagian ini. Klik :guilabel:`Tambah Anggaran` untuk membuat "
"anggaran baru untuk proyek."

#: ../../content/applications/services/project/project_dashboard.rst:87
msgid ""
":doc:`Analytic accounting </applications/finance/accounting/reporting/"
"analytic_accounting>` must be enabled in your database’s **Accounting** "
"application in order for this section to be displayed."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/services/project/project_dashboard.rst:94
msgid "Project updates"
msgstr "Pembaruan proyek"

#: ../../content/applications/services/project/project_dashboard.rst:96
msgid ""
"Project updates allow you to take a snapshot of the project’s overall status "
"at a given point in time, for example, during a periodic (weekly, bi-weekly, "
"or monthly) review. This allows you to compare specific data points, note "
"any aspects of the project that need improvement, and estimate if the "
"project is on or off track."
msgstr ""
"Pembaruan proyek memungkinkan Anda mengambil snapshot dari status "
"keseluruhan proyek pada titik waktu tertentu, misalnya, selama peninjauan "
"berkala (mingguan, dua mingguan, atau bulanan). Hal ini memungkinkan Anda "
"membandingkan poin data tertentu, mencatat aspek proyek yang perlu "
"perbaikan, dan memperkirakan apakah proyek berjalan sesuai rencana atau "
"tidak."

#: ../../content/applications/services/project/project_dashboard.rst:101
msgid ""
"To create a new project update, go to the project dashboard, "
"click :guilabel:`New`, and fill in the following fields:"
msgstr ""
"Untuk membuat pembaruan proyek baru, buka dashboard proyek, klik "
":guilabel:`Baru`, dan isi field berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/services/project/project_dashboard.rst:104
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Status`: Choose between :guilabel:`On Track`, :guilabel:`At "
"Risk`, :guilabel:`Off Track`, :guilabel:`On Hold`, and :guilabel:`Done`. "
"Once the status is set, a color-coded dot is displayed on the project’s "
"Kanban card, allowing the project manager to easily identify which projects "
"need attention."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Status`: Pilih antara :guilabel:`Sesuai Rencana`, "
":guilabel:`Berisiko`, :guilabel:`Tidak Sesuai Rencana`, :guilabel:`Ditunda`, "
"dan :guilabel:`Selesai`. Setelah status ditetapkan, titik berwarna "
"ditampilkan pada kartu Kanban proyek, memungkinkan manajer proyek dengan "
"mudah mengidentifikasi proyek mana yang memerlukan perhatian."

#: ../../content/applications/services/project/project_dashboard.rst:108
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Progress`: Manually input the completion percentage based on the "
"project's progress."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Kemajuan`: Masukkan persentase penyelesaian secara manual "
"berdasarkan kemajuan proyek."

#: ../../content/applications/services/project/project_dashboard.rst:109
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Date` and :guilabel:`Author`: These fields are automatically "
"filled in with appropriate information based on the user who created the "
"update and the current date."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Tanggal` dan :guilabel:`Penulis`: Field ini secara otomatis diisi "
"dengan informasi yang sesuai berdasarkan user yang membuat pembaruan dan "
"tanggal saat ini."

#: ../../content/applications/services/project/project_dashboard.rst:111
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Description`: Use this rich-text field to gather notes. Depending "
"on the project configuration (e.g., if the project is billable), this field "
"may be pre-filled with current information on aspects such as profitability, "
"budget, milestones, etc."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Deskripsi`: Gunakan field rich-text ini untuk mengumpulkan "
"catatan. Tergantung pada konfigurasi proyek (misalnya, jika proyek dapat "
"ditagih), field ini mungkin telah diisi sebelumnya dengan informasi terkini "
"tentang aspek seperti profitabilitas, anggaran, milestone, dll."

#: ../../content/applications/services/project/project_management.rst:3
msgid "Project management"
msgstr "Manajemen project"

#: ../../content/applications/services/project/project_management.rst:5
msgid ""
"Odoo Project uses the **Kanban** project management system. This means all "
"projects are broken down into tasks, which are categorized on a whiteboard "
"according to what production phase they are in."
msgstr ""
"Odoo Project menggunakan sistem manajemen proyek **Kanban**. Ini berarti "
"semua proyek dipecah menjadi tugas, yang dikategorikan pada papan tulis "
"sesuai dengan fase produksi mana mereka berada."

#: ../../content/applications/services/project/project_management.rst:8
msgid "Did you know?"
msgstr "Tahukah Anda?"

#: ../../content/applications/services/project/project_management.rst:10
msgid ""
"The word **Kanban** comes from Japanese and refers to the \"visual board\" "
"management method."
msgstr ""
"Kata **Kanban** berasal dari bahasa Jepang dan mengacu pada metode manajemen "
"\"papan visual\"."

#: ../../content/applications/services/project/project_management.rst:17
msgid ""
"Open the **Project** app and click :guilabel:`Create` to start a new "
"project. Enter a :guilabel:`Name` for your project and "
"click :guilabel:`Create Project`."
msgstr ""
"Buka aplikasi **Project** dan klik :guilabel:`Create` untuk memulai proyek "
"baru. Masukkan :guilabel:`Name` untuk proyek Anda dan klik :guilabel:`Create "
"Project`."

#: ../../content/applications/services/project/project_management.rst:20
msgid ""
"You can customize your existing **projects** from the dashboard by clicking "
"the drop-down toggle button (:guilabel:`⋮`) on your project's **card**."
msgstr ""
"Anda dapat menyesuaikan **proyek** yang ada dari dashboard dengan mengklik "
"tombol toggle drop-down (:guilabel:`⋮`) pada **kartu** proyek Anda."

#: ../../content/applications/services/project/project_management.rst:None
msgid "Project card"
msgstr "Kartu proyek"

#: ../../content/applications/services/project/project_management.rst:27
msgid "This enables a new menu divided into four parts:"
msgstr "Ini mengaktifkan menu baru yang dibagi menjadi empat bagian:"

#: ../../content/applications/services/project/project_management.rst:29
msgid ""
":guilabel:`View`: see an overview of your project's components, such as "
"its :guilabel:`Tasks`, :guilabel:`Milestones` and :guilabel:`Project "
"Updates`. Depending on which apps you have activated, more options may be "
"available, such as :guilabel:`Documents`. All uploaded files can be found "
"under this menu, as well as in the **Documents** app, "
"under :guilabel:`Projects`;"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`View`: lihat gambaran umum komponen proyek Anda, seperti "
":guilabel:`Tasks`, :guilabel:`Milestones` dan :guilabel:`Project Updates`. "
"Tergantung pada aplikasi mana yang telah Anda aktifkan, lebih banyak opsi "
"mungkin tersedia, seperti :guilabel:`Dokumen`. Semua file yang diunggah "
"dapat ditemukan di bawah menu ini, serta di aplikasi **Dokumen**, di bawah "
":guilabel:`Projects`;"

#: ../../content/applications/services/project/project_management.rst:33
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Reporting`: analyze your project's progress and profitability "
"through graphics and statistics;"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Reporting`: analisis kemajuan dan profitabilitas proyek Anda "
"melalui grafik dan statistik;"

#: ../../content/applications/services/project/project_management.rst:35
msgid ""
"**Color**: make a line of color appear on the left side of the card so that "
"your project is more recognizable;"
msgstr ""
"**Color**: membuat garis warna muncul di sisi kiri kartu sehingga proyek "
"Anda lebih mudah dikenali;"

#: ../../content/applications/services/project/project_management.rst:37
msgid ":guilabel:`Settings`: you can change the following:"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Pengaturan`: anda dapat mengubah hal berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/services/project/project_management.rst:39
msgid "the :guilabel:`Name` of the project;"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Nama` project;"

#: ../../content/applications/services/project/project_management.rst:40
msgid "the :guilabel:`Name of the tasks` found under that project;"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Nama tugas` yang ditemukan di bawah project tersebut;"

#: ../../content/applications/services/project/project_management.rst:41
msgid "the :guilabel:`Customer` for whom the project is intended;"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Pelanggan` yang dituju project;"

#: ../../content/applications/services/project/project_management.rst:42
msgid "the :guilabel:`Tags` used for filtering;"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Tag` yang digunakan untuk menyaring;"

#: ../../content/applications/services/project/project_management.rst:43
msgid "the :guilabel:`Company` responsible for the project;"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Perusahaan` yang bertanggung jawab atas project;"

#: ../../content/applications/services/project/project_management.rst:44
msgid "the employee designated as :guilabel:`Project Manager`;"
msgstr "karyawan yang ditunjuk sebagai :guilabel:`Manajer Project`;"

#: ../../content/applications/services/project/project_management.rst:45
msgid "the :guilabel:`Planned Date` of the project;"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Tanggal Direncanakan` project;"

#: ../../content/applications/services/project/project_management.rst:46
msgid "the total :guilabel:`Allocated Hours` for that project."
msgstr "total :guilabel:`Jam Dialokasikan` untuk project tersebut."

#: ../../content/applications/services/project/project_management.rst:48
msgid ""
"Additionally, you can mark the project as :guilabel:`Favorite`, allowing you "
"to find it using the :guilabel:`My Favorites` filter on the Kanban view;"
msgstr ""
"Selain itu, anda dapat menandai project sebagai :guilabel:`Favorit`, "
"memungkinkan anda menemukannya menggunakan filter :guilabel:`Favorit Saya` "
"pada tampilan Kanban;"

#: ../../content/applications/services/project/project_management.rst:None
msgid "Project settings"
msgstr "Pengaturan project"

#: ../../content/applications/services/project/project_management.rst:56
msgid ""
"`Odoo Tutorials: Customize projects <https://www.odoo.com/slides/slide/"
"customize-projects-3615?fullscreen=1>`_"
msgstr ""
"`Tutorial Odoo: Kustomisasi project <https://www.odoo.com/slides/slide/"
"customize-projects-3615?fullscreen=1>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/services/project/project_management.rst:59
msgid ""
"Further settings are available under the :guilabel:`Settings` tab. Most of "
"them are *only* available depending on the activated apps."
msgstr ""
"Pengaturan lebih lanjut tersedia di bawah tab :guilabel:`Pengaturan`. "
"Sebagian besar hanya tersedia tergantung pada aplikasi yang diaktifkan."

#: ../../content/applications/services/project/project_management.rst:63
msgid "Scheduling activities"
msgstr "Menjadwalkan aktivitas"

#: ../../content/applications/services/project/project_management.rst:65
msgid ""
"You can schedule **activities** (ex. :guilabel:`Call`, :guilabel:`Meeting`, "
"etc.) per project by clicking on the **clock** icon on a project. Doing so "
"opens a list with already scheduled activities and allows planning **new** "
"activities by clicking :guilabel:`+ Schedule an activity`. On the pop-up "
"window, select the :guilabel:`Activity Type`, enter a :guilabel:`Summary` "
"for that activity, a :guilabel:`Due Date`, and assign it to an employee. "
"According to the :guilabel:`Activity Type`, you may have **additional "
"options** available."
msgstr ""
"Anda dapat menjadwalkan **aktivitas** (misalnya :guilabel:`Panggilan`, "
":guilabel:`Rapat`, dll.) per proyek dengan mengklik ikon **jam** pada "
"proyek. Melakukan ini akan membuka daftar aktivitas yang sudah dijadwalkan "
"dan memungkinkan perencanaan aktivitas **baru** dengan mengklik :guilabel:`+ "
"Jadwalkan aktivitas`. Pada jendela pop-up, pilih :guilabel:`Jenis "
"Aktivitas`, masukkan :guilabel:`Ringkasan` untuk aktivitas tersebut, "
":guilabel:`Tanggal Jatuh Tempo`, dan tetapkan ke karyawan. Sesuai dengan "
":guilabel:`Jenis Aktivitas`, Anda mungkin memiliki **opsi tambahan** yang "
"tersedia."

#: ../../content/applications/services/project/project_management.rst:73
msgid ""
"If an activity is **already** scheduled, the icon may change to a **phone**, "
"**group of people**, or other."
msgstr ""
"Jika aktivitas **sudah** dijadwalkan, ikon dapat berubah menjadi "
"**telepon**, **kelompok orang**, atau lainnya."

#: ../../content/applications/services/project/tasks.rst:5
msgid "Task management"
msgstr "Manajemen task"

#: ../../content/applications/services/project/tasks/recurring_tasks.rst:3
msgid "Recurring tasks"
msgstr "Task rutin"

#: ../../content/applications/services/project/tasks/recurring_tasks.rst:5
msgid ""
"When handling a project, the same task often needs to be performed several "
"times: for example, weekly meetings or status reports. The **recurring "
"tasks** feature allows you to automate the creation of those tasks."
msgstr ""
"Ketika menangani project, tugas yang sama sering kali perlu dilakukan "
"beberapa kali: misalnya, pertemuan mingguan atau laporan status. Fitur "
"**tugas berulang** memungkinkan Anda mengotomatiskan pembuatan tugas "
"tersebut."

#: ../../content/applications/services/project/tasks/recurring_tasks.rst:10
msgid ""
"`Odoo Tutorials: Recurring tasks <https://www.odoo.com/slides/slide/"
"recurring-tasks-6958>`_"
msgstr ""
"`Odoo Tutorials: Tugas berulang <https://www.odoo.com/slides/slide/recurring-"
"tasks-6958>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/services/project/tasks/recurring_tasks.rst:15
msgid ""
"To enable recurring tasks, go to :menuselection:`Project --> Configuration --"
"> Settings`, then activate :guilabel:`Recurring Tasks`, and "
"press :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/services/project/tasks/recurring_tasks.rst:19
msgid "Set up task recurrence"
msgstr "Mengatur pengulangan tugas"

#: ../../content/applications/services/project/tasks/recurring_tasks.rst:21
msgid ""
"In an existing task, click the :icon:`fa-repeat` (:guilabel:`Recurrent`) "
"button next to the :guilabel:`Deadline` field. Then, configure "
"the :guilabel:`Repeat Every` field according to your needs."
msgstr ""
"Dalam tugas yang ada, klik tombol :icon:`fa-repeat` (:guilabel:`Berulang`) "
"di sebelah kolom :guilabel:`Batas Waktu`. Kemudian, konfigurasi kolom "
":guilabel:`Ulangi Setiap` sesuai kebutuhan Anda."

#: ../../content/applications/services/project/tasks/recurring_tasks.rst:25
msgid ""
"A new task in recurrence will be created once the status of the previous "
"task is set to :guilabel:`Done` or :guilabel:`Canceled`."
msgstr ""
"Tugas baru dalam pengulangan akan dibuat setelah status tugas sebelumnya "
"diatur ke :guilabel:`Done` atau :guilabel:`Canceled`."

#: ../../content/applications/services/project/tasks/recurring_tasks.rst:28
msgid ""
"The new task is created on the project dashboard with the following "
"configuration:"
msgstr "Tugas baru dibuat pada dashboard proyek dengan konfigurasi berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/services/project/tasks/recurring_tasks.rst:30
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Stage`: is set to the first stage of the project dashboard "
"(:guilabel:`New` or equivalent);"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Stage`: diatur ke tahap pertama dari dashboard proyek "
"(:guilabel:`New` atau yang setara);"

#: ../../content/applications/services/project/tasks/recurring_tasks.rst:32
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Name`, :guilabel:`Description`, :guilabel:`Project`, :guilabel:`Assignees`, :guilabel:`Customer`, :guilabel:`Tags`: "
"are copied from the original task;"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Name`, :guilabel:`Description`, :guilabel:`Project`, "
":guilabel:`Assignees`, :guilabel:`Customer`, :guilabel:`Tags`: disalin dari "
"tugas asli;"

#: ../../content/applications/services/project/tasks/recurring_tasks.rst:34
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Deadline`: is updated based on the :guilabel:`Repeat Every` field "
"(e.g., if the task is set to repeat once a week, 7 days will be added to the "
"deadline);"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Deadline`: diperbarui berdasarkan bidang :guilabel:`Repeat Every` "
"(misalnya, jika tugas diatur untuk berulang sekali seminggu, 7 hari akan "
"ditambahkan ke tenggat waktu);"

#: ../../content/applications/services/project/tasks/recurring_tasks.rst:36
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Milestones`, :guilabel:`Timesheets`, :guilabel:`Chatter`, :guilabel:`Activities`, :guilabel:`Subtasks`: "
"are **not** copied from the original task."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Milestones`, :guilabel:`Tabel Waktu`, :guilabel:`Chatter`, "
":guilabel:`Activities`, :guilabel:`Subtasks`: **tidak** disalin dari tugas "
"asli."

#: ../../content/applications/services/project/tasks/recurring_tasks.rst:39
msgid ""
"Once a recurrence is configured, a **smart button** on the task displays the "
"total number of existing recurrences."
msgstr ""
"Setelah pengulangan dikonfigurasi, sebuah **tombol pintar** pada tugas "
"menampilkan jumlah total pengulangan yang ada."

#: ../../content/applications/services/project/tasks/recurring_tasks.rst:43
msgid "Edit or stop task recurrence"
msgstr "Mengedit atau menghentikan pengulangan tugas"

#: ../../content/applications/services/project/tasks/recurring_tasks.rst:45
msgid ""
"**To edit** the recurrence, open the last task in recurrence. Any changes "
"made on the task will be applied to the tasks that will be created in the "
"future."
msgstr ""
"**Untuk mengedit** pengulangan, buka tugas terakhir dalam pengulangan. "
"Setiap perubahan yang dilakukan pada tugas akan diterapkan pada tugas yang "
"akan dibuat di masa mendatang."

#: ../../content/applications/services/project/tasks/recurring_tasks.rst:48
msgid ""
"**To stop** the recurrence, open the last task in recurrence and press "
"the :guilabel:`Recurrent` button next to the :guilabel:`Planned date`."
msgstr ""
"**Untuk menghentikan** pengulangan, buka tugas terakhir dalam pengulangan "
"dan tekan tombol :guilabel:`Recurrent` di samping :guilabel:`Planned date`."

#: ../../content/applications/services/project/tasks/sub-tasks.rst:3
msgid "Sub-tasks"
msgstr "Sub-task"

#: ../../content/applications/services/project/tasks/sub-tasks.rst:5
msgid ""
"When handling project tasks, you can often benefit from splitting the "
"workload into smaller **sub-tasks**, making it easier to track progress and "
"manage the work."
msgstr ""
"Saat menangani tugas proyek, Anda sering dapat memperoleh manfaat dari "
"membagi beban kerja menjadi **sub-tugas** yang lebih kecil, sehingga lebih "
"mudah melacak kemajuan dan mengelola pekerjaan."

#: ../../content/applications/services/project/tasks/sub-tasks.rst:8
msgid ""
"Odoo’s sub-task feature is particularly useful in some of the following "
"cases:"
msgstr "Fitur sub-tugas Odoo sangat berguna dalam beberapa kasus berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/services/project/tasks/sub-tasks.rst:10
msgid "The task workload is too big to handle in one record."
msgstr "Beban kerja tugas terlalu besar untuk ditangani dalam satu catatan."

#: ../../content/applications/services/project/tasks/sub-tasks.rst:11
msgid "There’s a clear sequence of steps to follow."
msgstr "Ada urutan langkah yang jelas untuk diikuti."

#: ../../content/applications/services/project/tasks/sub-tasks.rst:12
msgid ""
"Some parts of the workload fall under the scope of different projects and/or "
"assignees."
msgstr ""
"Beberapa bagian dari beban kerja berada dalam lingkup proyek dan/atau "
"penerima tugas yang berbeda."

#: ../../content/applications/services/project/tasks/sub-tasks.rst:14
msgid ""
"The original task to which sub-tasks are linked is referred to as the "
"**parent task**. The sub-tasks of the parent task are known as **child "
"tasks**."
msgstr ""
"Tugas asli yang ditautkan dengan sub-tugas disebut sebagai **tugas induk**. "
"Sub-tugas dari tugas induk dikenal sebagai **tugas anak**."

#: ../../content/applications/services/project/tasks/sub-tasks.rst:18
msgid "Creating sub-tasks"
msgstr "Membuat sub-tugas"

#: ../../content/applications/services/project/tasks/sub-tasks.rst:20
msgid "To create a sub-task:"
msgstr "Untuk membuat sub-tugas:"

#: ../../content/applications/services/project/tasks/sub-tasks.rst:22
msgid "Open the Project app, then go into your desired project."
msgstr "Buka aplikasi Project, lalu masuk ke proyek yang Anda inginkan."

#: ../../content/applications/services/project/tasks/sub-tasks.rst:23
msgid ""
"Click the task where you want to add the sub-task, then click "
"the :guilabel:`Sub-tasks` tab."
msgstr ""
"Klik tugas tempat Anda ingin menambahkan sub-tugas, lalu klik tab "
":guilabel:`Sub-tasks`."

#: ../../content/applications/services/project/tasks/sub-tasks.rst:24
msgid "Click :guilabel:`Add a line`, then fill in the :guilabel:`Title`."
msgstr "Klik :guilabel:`Add a line`, lalu isi :guilabel:`Title`."

#: ../../content/applications/services/project/tasks/sub-tasks.rst:25
msgid ""
