"are: :guilabel:`Title`, :guilabel:`Priority`, :guilabel:`Status`, "
"and :guilabel:`Assignees`. Use the :icon:`fa-sliders` (:guilabel:`sliders`) "
"icon to add or remove fields."
msgstr ""
"Anda dapat mengedit beberapa bidang sub-tugas langsung dari tab sub-tugas "
"tugas induk tanpa membuka sub-tugas individual. Secara default, yaitu: "
":guilabel:`Title`, :guilabel:`Priority`, :guilabel:`Status`, dan "
":guilabel:`Assignees`. Gunakan ikon :icon:`fa-sliders` (:guilabel:`sliders`) "
"untuk menambah atau menghapus bidang."

#: ../../content/applications/services/project/tasks/sub-tasks.rst:33
msgid ""
"Once the new sub-task is created, the following changes occur in the parent "
"task:"
msgstr ""
